Python Client for Cloud Text-to-Speech API
==========================================

|GA| |pypi| |versions| 

`Cloud Text-to-Speech API`_: Synthesizes natural-sounding speech by applying
powerful neural network models.

- `Client Library Documentation`_
- `Product Documentation`_

